item.description:
Last week we had a light turnout for frisbee on the common, but we had a good time and tossed around for about an hour. Hopefully the weather will be a bit more agreeable, and the shift from Wednesday to Thursday will yield a few more participants. As always, if the day and time does not work for you but you would be interested in joining, please email us to let us know what day(s) might be better.

I hope to see you there!
